但絕對有條件相信明天的明天的明天，腐化的高牆必有腐爛倒下的一日。我們不會坐着等，而是站出來行出來。<br />\n<br />\n我們已經從外殼脆弱易碎的雞蛋，蛻變成子彈打不破的水。細水長流，才會無堅不摧，一時間被困在水塔，終會讓坐在塔尖的人倒下來。<br />\n<br />\n懷着赤子之心的人，還沒有天真到幻想一步登天，堅持的代價就是耐性耐力。在對的路上，偶然也會犯錯，路程也特別漫長，會沮喪會失望，只要站在公義這一邊，就唔需要計較一時的得失。水無常形，不義的政權更比人生無常。<br />\n<br />\n我們付出所有力量，每次失敗其實都在培養更持久的能量。<br />\n<br />\n紀念回歸，要相信念念不忘，必有迴響；要保持力量，就要鬥命長。<br />\n<br />\n「走上不獻媚的路，腳步注定緩慢。」<br />\n<br />\n所以，要和喪屍鬥命長。  <br />\n<br />\n林夕 <br />\n電郵 :linxiapple@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n原文link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20190701/20717048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717048&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8Pd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=b5686f93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717048&h=3a16201a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20190701/20717048</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"歷史的巨輪再次轉動，一百年前清朝的滅忙就係1911年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2fa453b7c241bd6c03fd40d3c845853de55cd0","tid":1272003,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"［三毛五毛分化泛民又失敗］議員勸手足唔好衝，成分化題材<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1271949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1271949</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de0963d0a6cb649be74e0ea26751efe2d6c37d1a","tid":1272003,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"大家長命極 2047都係同一年死<br />\n真係不求同年同月同日生"},{"pid":"352f704638c53625c5dc5c5aa2a32dbb3b113427","tid":1272003,"uid":53610,"like":0,"